    contentAr: "العمل في خدمة العملاء يتطلب مجموعة محددة من المفردات والعبارات.\n\n## عبارات الترحيب\n\n- Thank you for calling. How may I assist you today?\n- I am happy to help you with that.\n- Thank you for your patience.\n\n## عبارات التوضيح\n\n- Could you please repeat that?\n- I want to make sure I understand correctly.\n- Would you mind spelling your name for me?\n\n## عبارات التعاطف\n\n- I completely understand your frustration.\n- I apologize for the inconvenience.\n- I can see why this would be upsetting.\n\n## عبارات حل المشكلات\n\n- Let me look into that for you right away.\n- I have found a solution for you.\n\n## التعامل مع العملاء الغاضبين\n\nابقَ هادئاً، لا تجادل، وركّز على الحلول لا المشاكل.",
    content: "Working in customer service requires a specific set of vocabulary and phrases.\n\n## Greeting Phrases\n\n- Thank you for calling. How may I assist you today?\n- I am happy to help you with that.\n- Thank you for your patience.\n\n## Clarification Phrases\n\n- Could you please repeat that?\n- I want to make sure I understand correctly.\n- Would you mind spelling your name for me?\n\n## Empathy Phrases\n\n- I completely understand your frustration.\n- I apologize for the inconvenience.\n- I can see why this would be upsetting.\n\n## Problem-Solving Phrases\n\n- Let me look into that for you right away.\n- I have found a solution for you.\n\n## Difficult Situations\n\nStay calm, never argue, and focus on solutions not problems."
